WEBVTT

00:00:09.633 --> 00:00:11.266
( birds chirping )

00:00:16.633 --> 00:00:19.200
( wind blowing )

00:00:24.566 --> 00:00:27.733
Man: TO BE QUIET
AND DO AS YOU'RE TOLD,

00:00:27.733 --> 00:00:29.466
THAT'S HOW COWARDS LIVE.

00:00:31.066 --> 00:00:34.166
DO YOU STAY DOWN, FIGHT BACK?

00:00:34.166 --> 00:00:36.200
( engine roaring )

00:00:38.300 --> 00:00:41.500
WHAT THE HELL AM I DOING?

00:00:41.500 --> 00:00:43.266
♪

00:01:10.773 --> 00:01:13.006
( glass clinks )

00:01:22.673 --> 00:01:24.273
DO I STAY DOWN HERE...

00:01:27.840 --> 00:01:30.006
OR FIGHT MY WAY OUT?

00:01:34.673 --> 00:01:37.406
( crowd roaring )

00:01:37.406 --> 00:01:38.440
( boxer grunts )

00:01:41.440 --> 00:01:42.606
( chuckles )

00:01:42.606 --> 00:01:43.706
( roars )

00:01:43.706 --> 00:01:45.940
( boxer #2 panting )

00:01:49.740 --> 00:01:51.140
( gasps )

00:01:53.773 --> 00:01:54.940
I'M STUCK.

00:01:54.940 --> 00:01:57.140
I CAN'T DO EITHER ONE.

00:02:08.513 --> 00:02:11.113
♪

00:02:11.113 --> 00:02:12.813
Woman: MEGALO‐BOXING
FUSES ATHLETICISM

00:02:12.813 --> 00:02:17.846
WITH INNOVATIVE GEAR TECHNOLOGY
TO CREATE THE FUTURE OF BOXING.

00:02:17.846 --> 00:02:19.413
IT'S EXCITING, RUGGED,

00:02:19.413 --> 00:02:21.746
AND IT'S THE PREMIERE FORM
OF ENTERTAINMENT,

00:02:21.746 --> 00:02:23.546
THE ULTIMATE COMBAT SPORT.

00:02:23.546 --> 00:02:29.180
TODAY, I UNVEIL THE LONG‐HELD
DREAM OF MY GRANDFATHER,

00:02:29.180 --> 00:02:32.246
WHO PRECEDED ME AS THE HEAD
OF THE SHIRATO GROUP,

00:02:32.246 --> 00:02:37.046
THE MEGALOBOX TOURNAMENT
KNOWN AS MEGALONIA!

00:02:38.513 --> 00:02:40.313
( crowd gasps )

00:02:40.313 --> 00:02:42.846
IT WILL GO BEYOND BORDERS
AND INSTITUTIONS,

00:02:42.846 --> 00:02:46.213
BECKONING ALL WHO WOULD CLAIM
THE MANTLE OF GREATEST FIGHTER.

00:02:46.213 --> 00:02:48.980
THE QUALIFYING ROUNDS
WILL BE GLOBAL,

00:02:48.980 --> 00:02:50.246
WITH ONLY FOUR COMPETITORS

00:02:50.246 --> 00:02:52.846
MAKING IT
INTO THE FINAL BRACKET.

00:02:52.846 --> 00:02:56.213
FIGHTING IN MEGALONIA MEANS
FIGHTING AT THE HIGHEST LEVEL,

00:02:56.213 --> 00:02:58.246
AND THAT MEANS
TRUE MEGALO‐BOXING.

00:02:59.913 --> 00:03:02.253
THE TOURNAMENT BEGINS
IN THREE MONTHS.

00:03:02.253 --> 00:03:05.186
WHO WILL END UP BEING
THE RIGHTFUL CHAMPION?

00:03:05.186 --> 00:03:08.086
THAT WILL BE DECIDED
IN THE RING.

00:03:12.553 --> 00:03:14.086
Mechanic: THERE.

00:03:18.486 --> 00:03:20.320
NOW, THEN...

00:03:20.320 --> 00:03:22.186
Reporter: SOME CRITICS CLAIM
THAT MEGALO‐BOXING

00:03:22.186 --> 00:03:24.420
IS LITTLE MORE
THAN VIOLENT SPECTACLE.

00:03:24.420 --> 00:03:25.320
YOUR THOUGHTS?

00:03:25.320 --> 00:03:27.286
Promoter:
WE CONSIDER IT A GLOBAL BENEFIT

00:03:27.286 --> 00:03:30.020
THAT PROMOTES COHESION
BETWEEN ALL SOCIAL LEVELS.

00:03:30.020 --> 00:03:33.620
THE POTENTIAL
OF GEAR TECHNOLOGY IS LIMITLESS,

00:03:33.620 --> 00:03:38.053
AND MEGALONIA WILL BE THE FIRST
STEP IN DEMONSTRATING THAT.

00:03:38.053 --> 00:03:39.453
Mechanic: I'M ALL FINISHED
FIXING UP YOUR GEAR.

00:03:39.453 --> 00:03:43.453
THE MOTORCYCLE'S
GONNA TAKE A BIT LONGER, THOUGH.

00:03:43.453 --> 00:03:44.620
( boxer crunching )

00:03:44.620 --> 00:03:46.020
JUST HOW THE HELL DID YOU MANAGE

00:03:46.020 --> 00:03:48.486
TO WRECK IT THAT BADLY, ANYWAY?

00:03:48.486 --> 00:03:50.320
Reporter: ...MOMENTS AGO THAT
YOU'D BE ACCEPTING COMPETITORS

00:03:50.320 --> 00:03:53.620
FROM ANY REGION OR ORGANIZATION.
ARE THERE ANY RESTRICTIONS?

00:03:53.620 --> 00:03:58.986
Yukiko: NO RESTRICTIONS ON AGE,
NATIONALITY, OR QUALIFICATIONS.

00:03:58.986 --> 00:04:02.293
MEGALONIA IS OPEN
TO ALL CITIZENS.

00:04:02.293 --> 00:04:03.026
( boxer scoffs )

00:04:05.960 --> 00:04:08.193
Yukiko: NOW I'D LIKE
TO INTRODUCE THE MAN

00:04:08.193 --> 00:04:10.860
WHO MIGHT BE CALLED THE STAR
OF THE MEGALONIA TOURNAMENT,

00:04:10.860 --> 00:04:12.660
ITS FIRST COMPETITOR.

00:04:12.660 --> 00:04:14.726
HE'S AN UNDEFEATED CHAMPION.

00:04:14.726 --> 00:04:16.193
HIS DOMINATING PROWESS

00:04:16.193 --> 00:04:18.926
HAS MADE HIM THE FAVORITE
TO WIN THIS COMPETITION.

00:04:18.926 --> 00:04:21.126
YOU COULD SAY
THAT HE'S THE EMBODIMENT...

00:04:21.126 --> 00:04:22.860
‐ ( boxer sighs )
‐ Yukiko: OF TRUE MEGALO‐BOXING.

00:04:22.860 --> 00:04:25.193
HE'S THE KING OF THE RING, YUR‐‐

00:04:26.526 --> 00:04:29.226
( boxer groans )

00:04:31.793 --> 00:04:33.593
Mechanic: HMM.

00:04:33.593 --> 00:04:35.126
YOU'RE NOT GONNA ENTER, THEN?

00:04:35.126 --> 00:04:37.926
Boxer: SHE SAID THAT IT'S OPEN
TO ALL "CITIZENS."

00:04:37.926 --> 00:04:39.926
DIDN'T YOU HEAR THAT PART?

00:04:41.526 --> 00:04:42.993
Mechanic: HMPH.

00:04:42.993 --> 00:04:45.326
SINCE WE DON'T
HAVE CITIZEN I. D. s,

00:04:45.326 --> 00:04:48.460
I GUESS THAT MAKES US
NON‐CITIZENS, THEN?

00:04:48.460 --> 00:04:49.826
EH, WHO CARES?

00:04:49.826 --> 00:04:51.893
THERE'S AN APPEAL
TO LIVING FREE,

00:04:51.893 --> 00:04:54.293
NOT BEING HELD DOWN
BY ANYTHING.

00:04:54.293 --> 00:04:55.760
IT'S FINE BY ME.

00:04:55.760 --> 00:04:57.926
( boxer chuckles )

00:04:57.926 --> 00:04:59.726
‐ ( crowd yelling )
‐ ( dogs barking )

00:04:59.726 --> 00:05:01.200
Man: YOU BETTER HURRY!

00:05:01.200 --> 00:05:04.266
GET YOUR ASS MOVING!
FASTER, YOU MANGY HOUND!

00:05:04.266 --> 00:05:07.466
YOU BETTER KEEP RUNNING,
OR IT'S THE SOUP POT FOR YOU!

00:05:07.466 --> 00:05:08.966
AFTER IT! GO! GO!

00:05:13.400 --> 00:05:14.800
DAMN.

00:05:14.800 --> 00:05:16.500
( tickets crinkling )

00:05:16.500 --> 00:05:17.600
( scoffs )

00:05:17.600 --> 00:05:20.866
LAST TIME I BET ON A STUPID DOG.

00:05:23.433 --> 00:05:24.700
Mechanic: HERE YOU GO.

00:05:24.700 --> 00:05:27.033
YOU SIGN THE INVOICE?

00:05:30.400 --> 00:05:35.100
HMPH. THE NAMELESS MAN
WHO ONLY GOES BY HIS RING NAME.

00:05:35.100 --> 00:05:39.033
MR. JUNK DOG,
YOUR REPAIRS ARE NOW COMPLETE.

00:05:39.033 --> 00:05:42.166
YOU KNOW, REAL BOXERS
ARE PROBABLY JUST LIKE YOU.

00:05:42.166 --> 00:05:44.900
CITIZENSHIP DOESN'T MAKE YOU
A BETTER ATHLETE.

00:05:44.900 --> 00:05:46.566
Junk Dog:
ENOUGH OF THE CRAZY TALK.

00:05:46.566 --> 00:05:48.366
WHAT DO I OWE YOU?

00:05:48.366 --> 00:05:50.300
Mechanic: THIS IS
THE THIRD TIME THIS MONTH

00:05:50.300 --> 00:05:52.800
YOUR TIP PAID OFF FOR ME,
SO LET'S CALL IT EVEN.

00:05:52.800 --> 00:05:54.433
( Junk Dog chuckles )

00:05:54.433 --> 00:05:57.766
THEN I SUGGEST YOU BET ON ME
WINNING TONIGHT FOR A CHANGE.

00:05:57.766 --> 00:05:59.906
( overlapping chatter )

00:06:03.173 --> 00:06:06.006
Man: YOU GUYS HEAR
ABOUT THIS MEGALONIA THING?

00:06:06.006 --> 00:06:08.106
Man #2: WHY SHOULD
I CARE ABOUT IT?

00:06:08.106 --> 00:06:11.273
Man #3: MAN, IF I WAS
JUST A BIT YOUNGER.

00:06:11.273 --> 00:06:13.806
♪

00:06:23.340 --> 00:06:24.140
Junk Dog: HUH?

00:06:31.840 --> 00:06:33.840
( pounding on door )

00:06:34.740 --> 00:06:36.873
Man: YO! 'SUP, JUNK DOG?

00:06:36.873 --> 00:06:40.240
YOU GOTTA MAKE YOUR DIVE
LOOK GOOD AGAIN TONIGHT.

00:06:40.240 --> 00:06:44.240
Junk Dog: SORRY, BUD.
TONIGHT, I'M GOING ALL OUT.

00:06:44.240 --> 00:06:45.840
Men: HMM?

00:06:45.840 --> 00:06:49.040
Man #2: DIDN'T OLD MAN NANBU
TELL YOU WHAT'S UP?

00:06:50.706 --> 00:06:52.673
Junk Dog: SON OF A BITCH.

00:06:52.673 --> 00:06:54.173
( Nanbu swallowing )

00:06:56.573 --> 00:06:58.773
( sighs )

00:07:02.513 --> 00:07:04.480
HMM?

00:07:04.480 --> 00:07:09.013
HEY, PARTNER! DID YOU COME
ALL THE WAY HERE TO PICK ME UP?

00:07:09.013 --> 00:07:12.513
OH, YOU'RE SUCH A SWEETHEART.
( weeps )

00:07:12.513 --> 00:07:13.946
I WAS WONDERING.

00:07:13.946 --> 00:07:15.646
COULD YOU MAYBE LET ME BORROW

00:07:15.646 --> 00:07:16.980
A LITTLE SOMETHIN‐‐HUH?

00:07:16.980 --> 00:07:19.613
Junk Dog:
START TALKING, POPS, RIGHT NOW.

00:07:19.613 --> 00:07:21.580
YOU PROMISED.
YOU SAID THERE'D BE

00:07:21.580 --> 00:07:24.480
NO SHADY CRAP
GOING DOWN TONIGHT.

00:07:24.480 --> 00:07:25.913
Nanbu: HAH! LOOK, MAN,

00:07:25.913 --> 00:07:28.146
YOU KNOW WE HELP EACH OTHER OUT,

00:07:28.146 --> 00:07:31.046
SO LET'S DROP THE SOCIAL GRACES
AND BE REAL.

00:07:31.046 --> 00:07:34.813
IT'S WHAT YOU MIGHT CALL
A SUDDEN CHANGE IN CIRCUMSTANCE.

00:07:34.813 --> 00:07:36.480
WHEN YOU FIGHT
FOR SERIOUS AND WIN,

00:07:36.480 --> 00:07:39.713
IT DOESN'T BRING IN ENOUGH CASH.
THEY THREATENED ME OVER IT.

00:07:39.713 --> 00:07:41.446
Junk Dog: SCREW THAT GARBAGE!

00:07:41.446 --> 00:07:44.746
I TOLD YOU. I'M SICK AND TIRED
OF THROWING THESE DAMN FIGHTS!

00:07:44.746 --> 00:07:46.313
Nanbu: ANSWER ME ONE QUESTION.

00:07:46.313 --> 00:07:50.813
HOW'S AN ILLEGAL MEGALO‐BOXER
WITH NO FAME AND NO I. D.

00:07:50.813 --> 00:07:52.813
SUPPOSED TO MAKE
SOME MONEY OTHERWISE?

00:07:56.713 --> 00:07:58.646
HMPH. YOU KNOW I'M RIGHT.

00:07:58.646 --> 00:08:01.520
YOU'RE TOO STRONG
FOR UNDERGROUND FIGHTS.

00:08:01.520 --> 00:08:03.686
NO ONE WANTS A BOXER IN THE RING

00:08:03.686 --> 00:08:06.120
SO GOOD HE MAKES
THE ODDS ONE‐SIDED.

00:08:10.053 --> 00:08:13.353
LOOK, JUST SUCK IT UP
A LITTLE BIT LONGER.

00:08:13.353 --> 00:08:16.920
NEXT TIME, I'LL TRY
AND GET YOU WHAT YOU'RE AFTER,

00:08:16.920 --> 00:08:20.253
A REAL MATCH WITH
A REAL OPPONENT, ALL RIGHT?

00:08:20.253 --> 00:08:21.720
( chuckles )

00:08:28.420 --> 00:08:30.786
( crowd yelling )

00:08:30.786 --> 00:08:34.620
Nanbu: IF YOU'RE HARD UP
OR A CHEAP‐ASS, YOU BET ON DOGS.

00:08:34.620 --> 00:08:36.786
BUT IF YOU'VE
SOME CASH TO SPARE,

00:08:36.786 --> 00:08:39.653
EVEN A LITTLE,
YOU BET ON PEOPLE.

00:08:39.653 --> 00:08:41.786
( crowd cheering )

00:08:45.353 --> 00:08:47.020
( footsteps )

00:08:53.386 --> 00:08:55.020
Nanbu: HEY.

00:08:56.386 --> 00:08:58.286
IT'S SHOWTIME.

00:08:58.286 --> 00:08:59.186
( earpiece click )

00:08:59.186 --> 00:09:00.926
♪

00:09:03.993 --> 00:09:06.526
Referee: THREE‐MINUTE ROUNDS
WITH NO ROUND LIMIT.

00:09:06.526 --> 00:09:07.560
( hydraulics hiss )

00:09:07.560 --> 00:09:09.326
WHO'S GONNA GET HIT SO HARD

00:09:09.326 --> 00:09:10.493
THEY PUKE BLOOD?!

00:09:14.126 --> 00:09:17.826
MAKING HIS FIRST APPEARANCE
AT THE DRUNK MONK, JUNK DOG!

00:09:17.826 --> 00:09:21.560
AND OUR HEADLINER,
GHETTO HACHIYA!

00:09:21.560 --> 00:09:23.826
THIS IS TONIGHT'S MAIN EVENT!

00:09:23.826 --> 00:09:25.493
IF YOU'VE GOT
ANY CASH LEFT ON YOU,

00:09:25.493 --> 00:09:27.593
NOW'S THE TIME TO COUGH IT UP!

00:09:27.593 --> 00:09:29.426
( man gags )
WOULD YOU GET A LOAD OF THAT?!

00:09:29.426 --> 00:09:30.760
WHAT'S WITH THAT GEAR?

00:09:30.760 --> 00:09:32.526
LOOKS LIKE
HE'S WEARING A SCRAPHEAP!

00:09:32.526 --> 00:09:35.993
Man #2: HACHIYA,
SMASH THAT KID AND HIS GEAR!

00:09:35.993 --> 00:09:37.460
( Nanbu on earpiece )
YOU REMEMBER THE PLAN, RIGHT?

00:09:37.460 --> 00:09:38.993
TOWARD THE END
OF THE THIRD ROUND

00:09:38.993 --> 00:09:41.093
WHEN THERE'S A MINUTE LEFT,
YOU'RE GONNA TAKE THE FALL.

00:09:41.093 --> 00:09:43.893
FEEL FREE TO GRAB THE LEAD
IN THE EARLY ROUNDS, OKAY?

00:09:43.893 --> 00:09:45.960
WORD IS,
THIS GUY'S A SLOW STARTER.

00:09:45.960 --> 00:09:49.460
JUST TAKE YOUR TIME,
AND DRAW HIM OUT. GOT IT?

00:09:49.460 --> 00:09:51.093
‐ ( bell rings )
‐ ( crowd yelling )

00:09:51.093 --> 00:09:53.660
Hachiya: WHAT IN THE HELL
ARE YOU WEARING?

00:09:53.660 --> 00:09:55.726
THAT'S SOME BUSTED‐ASS GEAR,
LITTLE DOGGIE,

00:09:55.726 --> 00:09:58.893
DEFINITELY
NOT A CROWD‐PLEASER.

00:09:58.893 --> 00:10:01.233
( thinking )
HE MUST BE SCREWING WITH ME.

00:10:01.233 --> 00:10:02.466
( Junk Dog grunts )

00:10:02.466 --> 00:10:06.033
( Hachiya grunting )

00:10:06.033 --> 00:10:08.666
YOU THOUGHT
I'D LET YOU TAKE THE LEAD?

00:10:10.066 --> 00:10:12.066
‐ ( Junk Dog scoffs )
‐ Cornerman: YEAH.

00:10:12.066 --> 00:10:13.566
( punches thumping )

00:10:13.566 --> 00:10:15.400
( Gear whirring )

00:10:19.433 --> 00:10:21.333
Nanbu: DAMN,
HE'S REALLY GOING FOR IT.

00:10:21.333 --> 00:10:23.466
SO MUCH FOR BEING
A SLOW STARTER.

00:10:23.466 --> 00:10:25.666
LISTEN UP.
CHANGE OF PLANS, PARTNER.

00:10:25.666 --> 00:10:28.000
PICK UP THE PACE,
AND PUSH HIM BACK.

00:10:29.533 --> 00:10:31.733
Junk Dog: EASY FOR YOU TO SAY.

00:10:35.933 --> 00:10:37.600
( chuckles )

00:10:40.033 --> 00:10:40.866
( Hachiya gasps )

00:10:43.166 --> 00:10:44.733
( gasps )

00:10:45.933 --> 00:10:48.466
( bell rings )

00:10:48.466 --> 00:10:50.600
( crowd gasps )

00:10:50.600 --> 00:10:52.666
( Hachiya shuddering )

00:10:54.100 --> 00:10:56.600
Cornerman: DAMN IT, THAT JERK
WAS JUST ROPE‐A‐DOPIN'!

00:10:56.600 --> 00:10:58.333
Junk Dog: THOUGHT SO.

00:10:58.333 --> 00:11:00.706
WITHOUT THE GEAR,
YOU'RE NO BOXER.

00:11:03.240 --> 00:11:04.740
Spectator: JUNK DOG!

00:11:04.740 --> 00:11:06.773
Spectator #2: I'M PUTTING
MY MONEY ON THE TRASH HEAP!

00:11:06.773 --> 00:11:08.873
Spectator #3:
SWITCH ME TO JUNK DOG!

00:11:08.873 --> 00:11:12.340
Nanbu: MAN, THIS IS
WHY PEOPLE HATE AMATEURS.

00:11:12.340 --> 00:11:13.740
Cornerman: HIS GEAR IS GARBAGE!

00:11:13.740 --> 00:11:15.206
Nanbu: GOING ALL OUT
IN AN UNDERGROUND MATCH

00:11:15.206 --> 00:11:16.340
THAT'S MOSTLY FOR GAMBLING,

00:11:16.340 --> 00:11:18.173
ONE WITH A FIXED OUTCOME,
AT THAT.

00:11:18.173 --> 00:11:21.973
IT'S NOT LIKE HE'S GONNA LOSE
EITHER WAY, YOU KNOW?

00:11:21.973 --> 00:11:23.040
( chuckles )

00:11:23.040 --> 00:11:24.173
Junk Dog: A ONE‐ROUND K. O.

00:11:24.173 --> 00:11:25.173
Nanbu: HUH?

00:11:25.173 --> 00:11:26.840
Junk Dog: IF IT WASN'T FIXED,

00:11:26.840 --> 00:11:29.740
THIS FIGHT WOULD HAVE
BEEN OVER WITH BY NOW.

00:11:34.273 --> 00:11:35.906
( Nanbu scoffs )

00:11:35.906 --> 00:11:37.673
( bell rings )

00:11:37.673 --> 00:11:41.973
Promoter: THE BETS ARE STARTING
TO FAVOR JUNK DOG WINNING THIS.

00:11:41.973 --> 00:11:44.273
GOTTA SAY
THE KID'S QUITE A PERFORMER.

00:11:44.273 --> 00:11:47.873
AND AS FOR MEGALO‐BOXING,
YOU'RE AS SMART AS THEY COME,

00:11:47.873 --> 00:11:51.140
JUST LIKE THE BOSS SAID.
( chuckles )

00:11:51.140 --> 00:11:54.706
PLUS, HE CAN PULL IT OFF
WEARING THAT PIECE OF JUNK.

00:11:54.706 --> 00:11:57.540
IF THE KID WASN'T WASTING AWAY
IN THIS HOLE, HE MIGHT HAVE

00:11:57.540 --> 00:11:59.473
‐ HAD A SHOT AT THE BIG TIME.
‐ Nanbu: HMM?

00:11:59.473 --> 00:12:01.580
Promoter: I'M TALKING
ABOUT MEGALONIA.

00:12:01.580 --> 00:12:04.046
JUST GETTING IN
SCORES YOU SOME GLORY,

00:12:04.046 --> 00:12:06.880
BUT THE CHAMPIONSHIP PURSE
WOULD SET YOU UP FOR LIFE,

00:12:06.880 --> 00:12:09.880
ENOUGH TO MOVE TO THE OTHER SIDE
OF THE TRACKS AND ENJ‐‐

00:12:09.880 --> 00:12:11.413
Nanbu: MR. DOMOTO...

00:12:11.413 --> 00:12:13.846
THE KID AND I ARE
JUST A COUPLE OF FRAUDS

00:12:13.846 --> 00:12:16.313
WHO ARE NEVER GONNA
BASK IN THAT MUCH SUNLIGHT.

00:12:16.313 --> 00:12:18.580
WE KNOW OUR PLACE
IN THE FOOD CHAIN.

00:12:18.580 --> 00:12:22.880
EARNING EASY MONEY LIKE THIS
IS MORE IN OUR WHEELHOUSE.

00:12:22.880 --> 00:12:24.580
( punches thumping )

00:12:24.580 --> 00:12:26.346
THERE'S LESS
THAN A MINUTE LEFT.

00:12:27.480 --> 00:12:30.313
GET READY TO WRAP THINGS UP.

00:12:30.313 --> 00:12:32.413
NOW LISTEN, PARTNER.

00:12:32.413 --> 00:12:34.513
LOSING TO THIRD‐RATE PUNKS
LIKE THIS JACKASS

00:12:34.513 --> 00:12:37.080
DOESN'T REFLECT POORLY
ON YOU, OKAY?

00:12:37.080 --> 00:12:39.513
YOU'VE GOT TRUE SKILL, SON,

00:12:39.513 --> 00:12:42.446
OR MY NAME ISN'T GANSAKU NANBU.

00:12:42.446 --> 00:12:45.113
( Junk Dog gags )

00:12:45.113 --> 00:12:47.713
( chuckles ) TRUE SKILL, HUH?

00:12:49.846 --> 00:12:51.680
WHAT BULLSHIT.

00:12:53.780 --> 00:12:56.680
‐ ( crowd cheering )
‐ ( ears ringing )

00:12:58.480 --> 00:12:59.720
( no audible dialogue )

00:13:01.853 --> 00:13:03.386
THEN AGAIN,

00:13:03.386 --> 00:13:05.386
WHAT DID I EXPECT?

00:13:13.053 --> 00:13:14.486
Domoto: GOOD WORK, MY FRIEND.

00:13:14.486 --> 00:13:18.153
I TOOK OUT THE INTEREST
FOR YOUR DEBTS, AS PER USUAL.

00:13:18.153 --> 00:13:20.386
Nanbu: OF COURSE, NO PROBLEM.

00:13:20.386 --> 00:13:21.720
Domoto: YOU KEEP THIS UP,

00:13:21.720 --> 00:13:24.086
AND YOU'LL CLEAN THE SLATE
IN NO TIME.

00:13:24.086 --> 00:13:25.786
BY THE WAY, I HEAR YOUR PARTNER

00:13:25.786 --> 00:13:27.886
WAS PRETTY PISSED OFF
