00:18:05.620 --> 00:18:08.420
Junk Dog: I'M SORRY
ABOUT HOW THAT MATCH TURNED OUT,

00:18:08.420 --> 00:18:09.586
BUT TODAY, I‐‐

00:18:09.586 --> 00:18:12.686
Mechanic: MY WIFE USED TO
