BE DIRT POOR BECAUSE OF IT.

00:18:17.653 --> 00:18:19.286
SPOT ON, HUH?

00:18:19.286 --> 00:18:21.453
Junk Dog: YOUR WIFE
SOME KIND OF FORTUNETELLER?

00:18:21.453 --> 00:18:25.986
