SHE RAN OFF A LONG TIME AGO.

00:18:25.986 --> 00:18:28.220
BUT, SEE, HERE'S THE THING.

00:18:28.220 --> 00:18:30.753
I CAN'T HELP BUT BELIEVE
IN THE PART OF ME

00:18:30.753 --> 00:18:32.453
THAT STILL BELIEVES, YOU KNOW?

00:18:32.453 --> 00:18:36.520
TAKE IT OR LEAVE IT,
IT'S JUST WHO I AM. SEE?

00:18:38.620 --> 00:18:39.953
( Junk Dog chuckles )

00:18:39.953 --> 00:18:43.253
MAN, YOU REALLY
ARE GONNA STAY DIRT POOR.

00:18:44.753 --> 00:18:47.653
( overlapping chatter )

00:18:47.653 --> 00:18:48.986
Nanbu: HEY.

00:18:51.020 --> 00:18:54.020
