00:19:01.393 --> 00:19:04.460
Junk Dog: YOU PROMISED
I COULD FIGHT FOR REAL TODAY.

00:19:04.460 --> 00:19:08.293
KEEP NAGGING ME, AND I'LL KNOCK
HIS ASS OUT IN THE FIRST ROUND.

00:19:08.293 --> 00:19:11.093
Nanbu: OKAY, FINE!
DO WHAT YOU WANT,

00:19:11.093 --> 00:19:14.193
BUT THIS ARRANGEMENT
IS FOR TODAY ONLY. GOT IT?

00:19:15.526 --> 00:19:16.926
DAMN.

00:19:16.926 --> 00:19:18.393
