GONNA KEEP US WAITING?

00:19:18.393 --> 00:19:21.626
HEY! SOMEONE DRAG
THAT BASTARD OUT HERE!

00:19:21.626 --> 00:19:23.326
IF HE'S CHICKENING OUT,

00:19:23.326 --> 00:19:26.060
