AND HAUL HIM INTO THE RING!

00:19:27.626 --> 00:19:29.660
Junk Dog: HEY, POPS.

00:19:29.660 --> 00:19:31.126
Nanbu: WHAT IS IT?

00:19:32.626 --> 00:19:36.760
Junk Dog: IF I SAID I WANTED TO
